lder injury in the lead-up to the Games, was24th fastest overall in the 40-swimmer strong field.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 750, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Le Clos\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"a shoulder injury\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 665}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead-up\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 693}, {\"ngram\": \"was24th\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"the 40-swimmer strong field\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I suffered a shoulder tear four weeks ago when a kid jumped on me when I was swimming and my shoulder popped out,\\\" he toldTeam SA's website before the swim.\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 880, \"end\": 882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.063355654981608e-13, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a shoulder tear\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"my shoulder\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"the swim\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It will have recovered but the inflammation and damage done has affected me.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the inflammation\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"damage\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three weeks ago I was crying every day.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will be devastated if I can not compete\\u2026 it will be one of the worst moments in my career.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the worst moments\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1107}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have put so much into it.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am now 32, a ballie, a pensioner in swimming terms.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a ballie\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"a pensioner\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming terms\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My body feels like it's 40.\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My body\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have bled for this sport, bled for my country.\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"my country\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a patriot.\\\"\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a patriot\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, the worst-case scenario played out for Le Clos, who could be seen rubbing his shoulder immediately after the race - clearly in discomfort.\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the worst-case scenario\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1339}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Clos\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"his shoulder\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"discomfort\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although this result almost certainly brings Le Clos' Olympic career to an end, before this race, he made it clear that he wasn't ready to retire.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this result\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Clos' Olympic career\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"an en