ouble gold at the 2013 world championships.\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"double gold\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2013 world championships\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the 2014 Commonwealth Games I won seven medals.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2014 Commonwealth Games\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"seven medals\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2015 at the world champs I won gold and silver.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world champs\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2051}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At Rio 2016 the silver should have been gold.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rio\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In 2017 I was world champ again and at the 2018 Commonwealth Games I won five medals.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2018 Commonwealth Games\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"five medals\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have also won 20 world short-course championship medals, the second most in the history of swimming.\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"20 world short-course championship medals\", \"from\": 2225, \"to\": 2266}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2298}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only Ryan Lochte has won more and I need three more medals (or two gold) to overtake him as short-course swimming GOAT.\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 